Mince the @garlic{1%clove}.

Whisk @lemon juice{1%Tbsp}, @water{2%Tbsp}, @white wine vinegar{2%Tbsp}, garlic, @honey{1%Tbsp}, and @sumac seasoning{1/2%tsp} in a #bowl{}.

Whisk and slowly drizzle in the @olive oil{1/2%cup} to combine.

Add @oregano{1%tsp}, @parsley{1%tsp}, @thyme{1/2%tsp}, @salt{1/4%tsp} and @pepper{1/2%tsp}.

Toss the vinaigrette into the salad and serve.
